SD=Fraud Diagnosis
CR= Fraud Diagnosis Analysis
BQs=CustomerBehavior EconomicModel AnalystReview
Analyze suspect transaction with Customer behavior information across product portfolio, using Expert Systems /Artificial Intelligence and/or manual review, including customer contact to determine if transaction is fraudulent. Further apply Economic Model to determine transaction disposition and notify applicable Product Fulfillment SDs.
Out of pattern card use is detected and the details passed for analysis. The analysis determines there is a high probability of fraud recommending appropriate containment actions
This service domain handles the evaluation of detected possible fraud to support an appropriate response to contain the exposure
CR - Fraud Diagnosis Analysis					BQ 1 - Customer Behavior	BQ 2 - Economic Model	BQ 3 - Analyst Review	
Ev	Up	Ex	Rq	Re	Re	Re	Rq	Re
EvCR Start a fraud diagnosis evaluation on a transaction
UpCR Update details for an active fraud diagnosis
ExCR Perform an automated action to an active diagnosis (e.g. upload additional data)
RqCR Request manual intervention for an active diagnosis (e.g. request access to analyst)
ReCR Retrieve details about a fraud diagnosis
ReBQ Retrieve details about a customer behavior analysis
ReBQ Retrieve details about an economic model analysis
RqBQ Request access to an analist for an active diagnosis
ReBQ Retrieve details about a analyst review of a transaction